<paragraph base="F45929558" id="IFRS16_84"><paranum>84</paranum><prolog><data name="standard_number" value="IFRS 16"/><data name="paranum" value="84"/></prolog><body><p id="IFRS16_P0288">The depreciation policy for depreciable <xref base="F45929849" href="IFRS16_APPA.dita#IFRS16_APPA/IFRS16_P0392">underlying assets<ph outputclass="def_xref"><xref keyref="GLOSSARY_DI0373"/></ph></xref> subject to <xref base="F45929764" href="IFRS16_APPA.dita#IFRS16_APPA/IFRS16_P0384">operating leases<ph outputclass="def_xref"><xref keyref="GLOSSARY_DI0269"/></ph></xref> shall be consistent with the lessor&#x2019;s normal depreciation policy for similar assets. A <xref base="F45929747" href="IFRS16_APPA.dita#IFRS16_APPA/IFRS16_P0382">lessor<ph outputclass="def_xref"><xref keyref="GLOSSARY_DI0222"/></ph></xref> shall calculate depreciation in accordance with <xref base="F47961122" href="../ias16/IAS16_TOC.dita#IAS16_TOC0001/IAS16_TOC0001_V2" id="IFRS16_X0299">IAS 16</xref> and <xref base="F47961123" href="../ias38/IAS38_TOC0001.dita#IAS38_TOC0001/IAS38_TOC0001_V2" id="IFRS16_X0300">IAS 38</xref>.</p></body></paragraph>